{"type": "article", "id": 2315, "title": "这个书桌是个音频放大器", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-11T21:29:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222212MTVw7BdSWJQcaobD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t韩国设计师 Jina U 日前推出了一款名为“ Soundbox ”的设计作品。正如它的名字，Soundbox 的确是一款音频放大器，但从外表来看，它又是一款极具复古风格的书桌。不管是竹制、木制还是陶瓷材质不插电源的音频放大器有很多种适合于摆放再桌面。而这款 Soundbox 却让桌子的侧柜承担了音频放大器的功能，与桌子完全融为一体。使用时，只需要将手机插入桌面的凹槽即可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052222109nGFxWqNKpSJa0BZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222211UfeqS26PrEoHsQRx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222211IYSQ6EGDWNmhM2Rb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}